item.title: Breadboard-Power-Supply-PCB-Design
item.description: Breadboard-Power-Supply-PCB-Design Welcome to the GitHub repository for my Breadboard Power Supply PCB Design project! This project aims to provide a compact and efficient solution for powering electronic circuits directly on a breadboard. This was design in KiCAD Description A power supply unit (PSU) is a device that converts alternating current (AC) power from an electrical outlet into direct current (DC) power suitable for powering electronic devices. The primary function of a power supply unit is to regulate and provide stable and reliable DC voltage and current to the components it serves.
